# GarminSights Frontend Environment Variables
#
# For local development: leave VITE_API_URL unset (or empty).  The Vite dev
# server proxies /api/* to http://localhost:8000, or the API client talks
# directly to it when VITE_API_URL is unset.
#
# For web/cloud deployment: set VITE_API_URL to your deployed backend URL
# before running `vite build`.  The value is baked into the static bundle at
# build time — no runtime env injection is needed on the frontend host.
#
# Example (production):
# VITE_API_URL=https://api.yourdomain.com

# VITE_API_URL=
